<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>写乎</strong>
<span>探究历史悬疑，挖掘地方风物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=d44f4524bf3d56abe2205ca5&lemmaId=425591&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/aec379310a55b3190703b31848a98226cefc17e0.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
红军史上最险的一战：漫川关生死大突围
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=d44f4524bf3d56abe2205ca5&lemmaId=425591&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
漫川关战斗，是关系到红四方面军生死存亡的一仗。当时，部队处境之险恶，战斗之惨烈是前所未有的。垭口高地上的松树枝叶被枪子和弹片削得光秃秃的，只剩下一根根半截子树桩。全军牺牲2000多人，219团团长韩亮臣也壮烈牺牲。34团一营五六百人，战斗结束时，只剩下80多人。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-10-19</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">209</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="07fff2d7140dfe26aa7aad10">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=62079b9e&authorId=67941b7cb01b76e17c42a420&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/ac6eddc451da81cbbd57fd405866d0160824318d.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>陈冠任</strong>
<span>中国历史学者，畅销书作家</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=07fff2d7140dfe26aa7aad10&lemmaId=425591&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/4b90f603738da977149c63d7ba51f8198718e39f.jpg" data-width="" data-height="" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_543bb29.png"></div>
<p class="title">
他本可和元帅当亲家，却一根筋犯犟；害得元帅失大将，自己也送命
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=07fff2d7140dfe26aa7aad10&lemmaId=425591&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
传说两人曾打过亲家，指腹为婚。后因双方均产下男婴，才没能结为亲家，便结成了干亲家。不巧的是，大革命时，二人因革命志向不同，分道扬镳。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-08-05</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">51</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="3e534ed05a6f4546fa54280b">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/usercenter/userpage?uk=62079b9e&authorId=77a062420dbb23d606bea920&from=lemma" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc7f6acb561db00baa1cc112a8a.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>婵稚翎</strong>
<span>著《国民党十大特种部队》</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<div class="no-cover">
<p class="title">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=3e534ed05a6f4546fa54280b&lemmaId=425591&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
“红军第一王牌”红1团大战敌3个团，敌师长被吓晕！
</a>
</p>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=3e534ed05a6f4546fa54280b&lemmaId=425591&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
1934年10月，红军主力一离开中央苏区，蒋介石几十万大军前堵后追。战功赫赫的红1军团作为主力，走在长征红军中的最前面，负责开路，而杨得志为团长的红1团又奉命担任红1军团的开路先锋，承担着用鲜血和性命为几万红军闯关开路的重任。</a>
</p>
</div>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-07-29</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">34</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
